settings.title: A healthy alternative to traditional catering
settings.slideshow_subsubtitle: Most of the time when you think of catering, you think of bad-tasting, unhealthy food. Not with mealfit. We take pride in making healthy, REAL food taste amazing.

settings.title: Keep you and your family out of the Drive thru
settings.slideshow_subsubtitle: m e a l f i t Meals make life easier... and healthier. Our home-cooked meals are perfectly portioned and packed with the nutrition your body needs.

settings.title: Make your next event unforgettable
settings.slideshow_subsubtitle: Do you have a fundraiser or big gathering you need to cook for? Or maybe you just want to tailgate like a boss. We can help.

settings.title: Show Up and Sell
settings.text: We take care of everything: set up, food, dishes, drinks and even dessert. Call or text us to order.

settings.promo_banner_subtext: Everything you need to shop, prep, and cook incredible meals. Our plans are the perfect way to jump start your fitness routine to maximize results.
Make your gym stand out from the competition and let mealfit become your nutrition coach.

settings.home_cta_subtext: We specialize in making your life easier. We want to take the stigma out of healthy food tasting bad. We take a southern style and make it healthier than your typical down south cuisine.

settings.title: Church Picnic to Tailgating, and Every Event in Between
settings.text: We deliver to your location and coach you on using the pit, then we're back for clean up and pick up. This is a turnkey process.

settings.title: Keep Your Team at the Office
settings.text: Boost productivity and honor your team by feeding them a great, working lunch on you– all while staying in house.
